852
00:54:35,139 --> 00:54:36,838
Hei, mana bisa mereka mencetak home run?

853
00:54:36,838 --> 00:54:38,349
Sudah bagus kalau mereka bisa memukul.

854
00:54:38,608 --> 00:54:40,749
Memang tahu apa kau soal baseball?

