00:54:42,019 --> 00:54:43,349
Kurasa tidak.

856
00:54:43,919 --> 00:54:45,189
Hei, maknae.

857
00:54:45,189 --> 00:54:46,189
Aku akan...

858
00:54:46,919 --> 00:54:48,159
