859
00:54:48,159 --> 00:54:49,389
- Nona Yoon.
- Ya.

860
00:54:49,389 --> 00:54:51,088
- Buatkan aku kopi.
- Baik.

861
00:54:51,329 --> 00:54:52,659
Apa kataku?

862
00:54:52,659 --> 00:54:53,959
Hasilnya sudah jelas.

